		{
			description: ["Blood Magic converts Life Points sacrificed at the Blood Altar into crafted power. The altar's tier determines which recipes are available — each tier requires Reinforced, Infused, Demonically Infused, or Ethereal Slates placed as upgrades. Begin by building the altar using the Sacrificial Orb to self-sacrifice, then accumulate LP to start slate progression. The altar is your Blood Magic laboratory for everything that follows."]
			id: "099035739255D6E7"
