		{
			dependencies: ["099035739255D6E7"]
			description: ["The Blood Altar is the core Blood Magic crafting block and the entry point for the entire mod. In this pack it requires Manasteel Ingots rather than Gold, firmly gating it behind Botania progression. Once built, surround it with Rune of the Dagger, Speed Runes, and Sacrifice Runes to accelerate LP generation. Altar tier determines recipe access — tier 1 is the beginning, not the ceiling."]
			id: "AL01000000000004"
