		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000004"]
			description: ["Blank Slates are the first step in the Blood Magic upgrade tier chain. An unadorned piece of smooth stone is soaked in the Blood Altar at tier 1, consuming LP to infuse it with bound blood magic. Slates progress through four grades — Blank, Reinforced, Imbued, Demonic, and Ethereal — each requiring more LP and a higher altar tier. Advancing the altar's slate tier unlocks progressively more powerful crafting recipes and higher maximum LP storage."]
			id: "AL01000000000005"
