		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000005"]
			description: ["The Sigil of the Fast Miner accelerates mining speed while held or stored in a Sigil of Holding. It drains LP from your bound network continuously while active — a meaningful cost that makes managing your blood infrastructure necessary, not optional. Pair with passive LP regeneration rituals so active sigils do not drain you dry during extended mining sessions. The Sigil of the Fast Miner is the first practical return on your LP investment."]
			id: "AL01000000000006"
