		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000005"]
			description: ["The Sigil of Air grants sustained levitation — a toggle-mode sigil that drains LP at a flat rate while airborne. Flight in Blood Magic carries a direct LP cost, making blood network infrastructure necessary before it is usable for extended exploration. The Sigil of Air effectively gates aerial travel behind a functioning LP generation system. It is one of the most powerful mobility tools in the early-magic stack, but it will drain an unprepared network dry within seconds."]
