		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000006", "AL01000000000007"]
			description: ["The Ritual Diviner is a wand that places Ritual Stones in the correct pattern for a given ritual when used on a Master Ritual Stone. Without it, ritual layouts require exact memorization or an external reference chart. Blood Magic rituals include passive LP regeneration from nearby mobs, crop growth acceleration, mob binding for will crystal generation, and dungeon summoning. The Diviner removes the barrier between wanting a ritual and having it."]
			id: "AL01000000000008"
