		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000008"]
			description: ["Living Armor is Blood Magic's endgame protective system — armor that grows and adapts based on your behavior. A fresh set starts with no inherent stats; upgrades are applied by binding training data from damage received, mining speed, and LP usage into upgrade points. Over time it becomes one of the most effective armor sets in the pack: customizable, upgradeable, and integrated directly into your blood network. The upgrade core is the seed."]
