		{
			description: ["Ars Nouveau runs on Source — a magical energy generated by Sourcelinks placed near plants, fires, Mana Jars, or Lily Pads of Fertility. Source Gems are crystallized Source, used for crafting glyphs, armor, and Enchanting Apparatus recipes. The entire Ars Nouveau material chain begins with generating Source: build Sourcelinks and a Source Jar before attempting any further AN progression. Without Source, the mod is a locked door."]
			id: "AL01000000000010"
