		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000010"]
			description: ["The Enchanting Apparatus is Ars Nouveau's primary crafting block. Surround it with Pedestals loaded with reagent items, supply Source from a linked Source Jar, and place the input item in the center slot — the Apparatus processes everything into the crafted output. All high-tier Ars Nouveau gear, spellbooks, and unique materials pass through the Apparatus. Build it once and use it for the entire magic tech tree."]
