		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000011"]
			description: ["The Alchemist's Crown is a mid-tier Ars Nouveau armor piece crafted at the Enchanting Apparatus. Wearing it reduces the Source cost of active spells. Wearing two or more pieces of the Alchemist's set grants passive Source regeneration based on nearby Sourcelinks. The crown unlocks the armor tier — completing the full Alchemist set (crown, robes, leggings, boots) makes a Source-efficient caster capable of sustained combat spellcasting without Source depletion."]
