		{
			description: ["Mine & Slash's Alchemy profession converts gathered herbs into potions at the Alchemy Station. Unlike combat skills, Alchemy levels up exclusively by crafting potions — not by killing mobs. Each brew awards profession experience, and higher alchemy levels unlock more potent recipe tiers. Potions scale with profession level, making a dedicated Alchemy build the single highest-leverage support investment for endgame atlas map content."]
			id: "6AF61DE43B13E826"
			rewards: [{
				auto: "enabled"
