		}
		{
			dependencies: ["6AF61DE43B13E826"]
			description: ["Mine & Slash herbs spawn in the overworld and inside dungeon maps. Collect them by right-clicking — no specific tool required. The Alchemy Station opens a recipe interface where you combine herbs in patterns to produce the intended potion tier. Begin with the lowest-tier health or mana potion and work upward through energy, resistance, and speed potions as your profession level increases. Consistency of brewing matters more than any single recipe."]
			id: "AL01000000000013"
