		{
			dependencies: ["AL01000000000013"]
			description: ["At Alchemy level 10, resistance and regeneration potions unlock. By level 20, speed and power variants become available. At level 30, the full potion roster is accessible — including endgame attribute potions that stack additively on top of Mine & Slash gear affixes. A high-level alchemist stocking their own supply has a decisive advantage in high-tier atlas maps: potions are the difference between clearing the opening room and dying in it."]
