			description: ["Blood sustains the altar. Source powers the apparatus. Herbs fill the flasks. Three alchemical traditions — each complete in itself, each contributing to a different axis of power. The convergence of all three is not a milestone. It is a method. The Grand Alchemist does not choose a discipline. They master the interplay between them."]
